---
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contribute - Skillsets.cc">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8 border-b border-border-ink pb-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-medium font-serif text-text-ink">Contribute a Skillset</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="border border-border-ink bg-stone-50 p-8 rounded-none mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif mb-4 text-text-ink border-b border-border-ink pb-2 inline-block">What We're Looking For</h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4 font-serif leading-relaxed">
        Unlike atomic skill marketplaces or limited examples, skillsets.cc indexes
        <strong class="text-text-ink">production-verified workflows</strong> — validated combinations
        of skills, agents, prompts, and configurations that have shipped real software.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border border-transparent p-8 rounded-none mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif mb-6 text-text-ink">Submission Process</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-orange-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold font-mono">
            1
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-serif text-text-ink mb-2">Download the Audit Skill</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary mb-3 font-serif">
              Get the <code class="bg-white border border-border-ink px-2 py-1 rounded-none font-mono text-xs">/audit_skillset</code> skill
              to validate your submission structure.
            </p>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/skillsets-cc/main/tree/main/tools/audit_skillset"
              class="text-orange-500 font-mono font-bold hover:underline"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
              Download Audit Skill →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-orange-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold font-mono">
            2
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-serif mb-2 text-text-ink">Prepare Your Skillset</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary mb-3 font-serif">
              Create a folder with the following structure:
            </p>
            <pre class="bg-white border border-border-ink p-4 rounded-none text-sm overflow-x-auto"><code>your-skillset/
├── skillset.yaml          # Manifest (required)
├── README.md              # User instructions (required)
├── PROOF.md               # Production evidence (required)
└── content/               # Files to install
    └── ...your files...</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-orange-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold font-mono">
            3
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-serif mb-2 text-text-ink">Run the Audit</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary mb-3 font-serif">
              Execute <code class="bg-white border border-border-ink px-2 py-1 rounded-none font-mono text-xs">/audit_skillset</code> in Claude Code
              to generate an <code class="bg-white border border-border-ink px-2 py-1 rounded-none font-mono text-xs">AUDIT_REPORT.md</code>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-orange-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold font-mono">
            4
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-serif mb-2 text-text-ink">Open a Pull Request</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary mb-3 font-serif">
              Submit your skillset to the registry with the audit report and production proof.
            </p>
            <a
              href="https://github.com/skillsets-cc/main"
              class="text-orange-500 font-mono font-bold hover:underline"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
              View Registry →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-orange-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold font-mono">
            5
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-serif mb-2 text-text-ink">Review & Merge</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary font-serif">
              Maintainers will review your production proof and validate the audit report.
              Once approved, your skillset will be published to the registry.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-orange-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold font-mono">
            6
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-serif mb-2 text-text-ink">Be Patient!</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary font-serif">
              Feel the urge to complain about how long it takes to get your material reviewed,
              but then realize this is just one guy trying to do something nice for the community—so
              you sign up as a co-maintainer.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border border-border-ink bg-stone-50 p-8 rounded-none mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif mb-4 text-text-ink border-b border-border-ink pb-2 inline-block">Example: Good Submission</h2>
      <div class="bg-white border border-border-ink p-4 rounded-none font-mono text-sm">
        <p class="text-text-secondary mb-2"><strong class="text-text-ink">The_Skillset</strong> by @supercollectible</p>
        <p class="text-text-secondary mb-2">
          Spec-driven SDLC with adversarial review, quality gates, and multi-model validation.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-tertiary">
          Tags: sdlc, planning, multi-agent, adversarial-review
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-orange-500 font-bold mt-2">
          ✓ Production URL verified<br />
          ✓ Audit report complete<br />
          ✓ Complete documentation
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border border-transparent p-8 rounded-none mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold font-serif mb-4 text-text-ink">Requirements</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-text-secondary font-serif">
        <li><strong class="text-text-ink">Production Proof:</strong> URL to a live product or repository showing real usage</li>
        <li><strong class="text-text-ink">Complete Documentation:</strong> Clear README with installation and usage instructions (the first <code class="bg-white border border-border-ink px-2 py-1 rounded-none font-mono text-xs"># heading</code> is stripped—it's shown in the page header)</li>
        <li><strong class="text-text-ink">Valid Schema:</strong> Must pass <code class="bg-white border border-border-ink px-2 py-1 rounded-none font-mono text-xs">skillset.yaml</code> validation</li>
        <li><strong class="text-text-ink">Audit Report:</strong> Generated by the official audit skill</li>
        <li><strong class="text-text-ink">Verification-First:</strong> High friction ensures high quality</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <a
        href="https://github.com/skillsets-cc/main/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md"
        class="text-orange-500 font-mono font-bold hover:underline"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
      >
        Read Full Contributing Guide →
      </a>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
